ETH EMPERRO'S EWN SHLMC

EynaOT yares oga teher wsa na Emrpeor ohw wsa so xveselisyec fnod fo
new olhctes, atth eh psnet all sih noyme ni sdres. He idd otn ehfmils
buorlte ni teh letas otbau sih eiosrdls; nro idd eh reca to go eiterh eho
tt thaetre or teh chsae, peectx for teh uitonieptrspo htne ffadroed ihm
for dsipygnila sih new olhctes. He hda a dirfeefnt utsi for echa hruo fo
teh yda nad sa fo nay oterh nikg or emrpeor noe si cstaecodmu to ysa,
“eh si nigttsi ni cui”nocl it wsa alwysa siad fo ihm, “eTh Emrpeor si
nigttsi ni sih ardwrboe.”

