wrko, b roetanaitl tniifiocdmao or aiitddnos or edeoilnst to toPj
nyacre eGgeurnbttm wrko, nad c nay cfteeD yuo teaociecsuSn


  2  Inrtafmonio otbau teh Msisnio fo jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm

jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm si synnoymous itwh teh eref dtsiriubtnio fo
ltceniocre wrkos ni rtafmos aaedelbr yb teh ewitsd yitarev fo mpcrotues
nicluidng sotbleoe odl eilddmaegd nad new psomteucr  tI ixstes
eeucbsa fo teh reftfos fo dehnurds fo evreutlnos nad dnoatnios rofm
epeolp ni all lkaws fo ueeltsio

efrlnV nad ncilfnaai pspuort to orpiedv evreutlnos itwh teh
staesnasci tehy eden si latciicr to rechanig jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm's
goals nad ensurnig atth teh jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm tllcceonio 
lilwremani flreey laivalaeb for aorgeeitnsn to coem  In 1002 teh jcoPtre
eGgeurnbt Lyrrteai evichrA Foundatnio wsa crteaed to orpiedv a rua
cnedse rpemnaent rueutf for jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm nad rueutf aorgeeitnsn.
To laern emor otbau teh jcoPtre eGgeurnbt Lyrrteai evichrA Foundatni
onad hwo yuor reftfos nad dnoatnios cna ehlp ese tceoSsni 3 nad ad
4n teh Foundatnio ewb paeg at 
