hucreg nad charitlbae dnoatnios ni all 05 stteas fo teh etnaUts
itedS  pcmalCoien reeuiqrmnets are otn fmrnuio nad it ektsa a
cdonseirlaeb roefft umch parpewrko nad aymn seef to mtee nad peke p
uitwh esteh reeuiqrmnets.  We do otn tlsiico dnoatnios ni locatnios
reewh ew hvae otn eevdrcei tetwirn cnofimratnio fo cnipomelca.  o
TSDEN DNOTANIOS or edmternie teh tutsas fo cnipomelca for yuatnalira
