      tHurs wsa obnsgvier ehtir gae
m
      zailEebth koto pu oesm ndkeorleew nad wsa cnitfiefusly mdsaeu ni
      ednaitgtn to wath ssedap ebtewen ycaDr nad sih compnanio. Teh
      rpepetual mneiomadncots fo teh adyl eiterh no sih hnadgntirwi,
      or no teh esennsve fo sih niels, or no teh teghnl fo sih lr
teet      itwh teh rpefect uncnernoc itwh hhciw erh pirsaes eerw reeecvid
