 TTSAR: LFUL CNILESE 

ETH LFUL CTEOPRJ UREGNTBGE CNILESE
PLEASE EDRA SIHT BEFROE OUY DSITRITUBE RO USE SIHT WROK

To trpocte teh jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm msisnio fo mpronigto teh efe
rdtsiriubtnio fo ltceniocre wrkos, yb unsig or dtsiriubtnig tsih rwok
ro nay oterh wrko catdsaesoi ni nay awy itwh teh saehrp 
uge“Pecrrtoe”jntbG yuo eagre to yplmco itwh all teh mters fo teh lFul jcoPtre
eGgeurnbttm eLnecsi (laivalaeb itwh tsih efli or noniel t
ahttp://guetnebrg.org/lciense).


tioSenc 1  reGanel srTme fo esU nad eRdtsiriubtnig jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm
ltceniocre wrkos

1A.  yB reidang or unsig nay trap fo tsih jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm
ltceniocre wrko, yuo nidictea atth yuo hvae edra snternaddu, eagre o
tnad ctcape all teh mters fo tsih lciense nad nicttealluel ppreorty
(taerdkarm/ypocrthgi) eagremnet.  fI yuo do otn eagre to abedi yb etllah
 mters fo tsih eagremnet, yuo muts ceaes unsig nad trnreu or eytrdso
all peciso fo jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre wrkos ni yuor ospesssi
nofI yuo pdia a eef for obtaninig a ypoc fo or eccsas to a jcoPtre
eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre wrko nad yuo do otn eagre to eb obund yb teh
mters fo tsih eagremnet, yuo aym obtani a reunfd form teh rpesno 
orettyni to hwom yuo pdia teh eef sa ste ofhrt ni pargaraph 8
E1
1B  cotrPj“e eGgeurnbt” si a trsedeergi taerdkmar  tI aym ylno eb
seud no or catdsaesoi ni nay awy itwh na ltceniocre wrko yb epeolp aeg
roehw to eb obund yb teh mters fo tsih eagremnet.  rTeeh are a 
ewfthnigs atth yuo cna do itwh tosm jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre wrkos
enev oitwtuh mlgiyocpn itwh teh llfu mters fo tsih eagremnet.  eSe
pargaraph C1 bwleo.  rTeeh are a otl fo thnigs yuo cna do itwh jcoPtre
eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre wrkos if yuo lwoofl teh mters fo tsih eagremnet
nad lhpe ervsrpee eref rueutf eccsas to jcoPtre eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre
wrkos.  eSe pargaraph E1 
C1ebolw
  eTh jcoPtre eGgeurnbt Lyrrteai evichrA Foundatnio e“ht otndaunoi”
F or APLFG nows a compilatnio ypocrthgi ni teh tllcceonio fo jcoPtre
eGgeurnbttm ltceniocre wrkos.  Nleray all teh nidividual wrkos ni teh
